---
title: Ventures for Shared Prosperity
---

{% extends "layouts/base.njk" %}

{% block masthead %}
  {{ super() }}
  <div class="hero hero--centered standard-restricted-width">
    <h1 class="hero__title">
      Ventures for Shared Prosperity
    </h1>
    <p class="hero__body g-max-3-half g-centered">
      With support from Wells Fargo we’re recruiting entrepreneurs to build 
      businesses that address the excess costs of poverty. We’re looking for 
      people that know if given the time, the money, and the audience, they 
      can channel their lived experiences, ideas, and talents into positive 
      impact. 
    </p>
    <p>
      <a href="/apply" class="btn hero__btn">Apply to be a founder</a>
    </p>
  </div>
  <img class="masthead__graphic masthead__graphic--centered" src="/images/masthead-graphic-triangle-subtle.svg" alt="" />
{% endblock %}

{% block main %}
<div class="standard-restricted-width">
  <header class="content-block__intro">
    <h2>Mission</h2>
    <p>
      We need this gig! We're on a mission from God.
    </p>
  </header>

  <header class="content-block__intro g-max-3">
    <h2>What we provide</h2>
    <p>
      We don’t have all the answers and we won’t have it all figured out when you 
      join us. But we know it takes a solid foundation to build a thriving technology 
      business. We provide that foundation.
    </p>
  </header>

  <ul class="home-benefits__list g-max-3">
    <li>
      <h3>Compensation</h3>
      <p>
        We pay a $75k annual salary and provide health benefits
        so you can focus on the work.
      </p>
    </li>
    <li>
      <h3>Expertise</h3>
      <p>
        We surround you with a team of seasoned experts so you can build
        world-class digital products.
      </p>
    </li>
    <li>
      <h3>Energy</h3>
      <p>
        We lift you up with encouragement, feedback, and kindness so you can bring
        your best self to the process.
      </p>
    </li>
  </ul>
</div>
{% endblock %}
